{"title":"Wolf Tooth Aero Chainrings for SRAM Cranks","link":"https://theradavist.com/wolf-tooth-aero-chainrings-for-sram-cranks/","date":1715691659000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"6000\" height=\"4000\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Wolf-Tooth_Aero-Chainring-for-107-BCD_2.jpg?fit=1200,4000&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Wolf-Tooth_Aero-Chainring-for-107-BCD_2.jpg?w=6000&amp;quality=75 6000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Wolf-Tooth_Aero-Chainring-for-107-BCD_2.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Wolf-Tooth_Aero-Chainring-for-107-BCD_2.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Wolf-Tooth_Aero-Chainring-for-107-BCD_2.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Wolf-Tooth_Aero-Chainring-for-107-BCD_2.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Wolf-Tooth_Aero-Chainring-for-107-BCD_2.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Earlier this year, Wolf Tooth announced aero chainrings for Shimano cranks and this week, the brand released its chainrings for use with <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1f8f513b-b98b-4cf0-abf5-e477c8747e9c&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fcollections%2Faero-chainrings\" target=\"_blank\">SRAM gravel and road cranksets</a>. Just like the Shimano rings, these SRAM rings were designed with performance in mind and feature a clean, integrated look that matches the profile of the crankarm or spider. New sizes include 46, 48, 50, and 52T depending on mount. They are compatible with most 12-speed chains and optimized for SRAM Eagle and Flattop chains, including Transmission. All Wolf Tooth chainrings are machined with 7075-T6 aluminum at Wolf Tooth in Minnesota, USA.</p>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1f8f513b-b98b-4cf0-abf5-e477c8747e9c&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolftoothcomponents.com%2Fcollections%2Faero-chainrings\" target=\"_blank\">Wolf Tooth</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/wolf-tooth-aero-chainrings-for-sram-cranks/\">Wolf Tooth Aero Chainrings for SRAM Cranks</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"3d3abb5ce5e3c0048acdc26466d581ae42ea7462c1103c49fe9f9fdd133591f0","category":"Cycling"}